message:
Unforgettable energy & enthusiasm at the rally in Allahabad. My gratitude to all Karyakartas & those who joined us. 

Talked at length about the efforts of the NDA government over the last 2 years particularly for the farmers, youngsters & the poor. Be it creating infra, powering villages & ending corruption, NDA is leaving no stone unturned for #TransformingIndia.
